Package: KinBN
Type: Package
Title: Kinship analysis based on a Bayesian network
Version: 2.1.0
Author: Chie Morimoto <kinbnsoftware@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Chie Morimoto <kinbnsoftware@gmail.com>
Description: KinBN is a free software for kinship analysis based on a Bayesian network. It can be applied to s hort tandem repeat (STR) markers commonly used in forensic genetics and calculates likelihood ratio.
License: GPL (>=3)
Encoding: UTF-8
